blog.description: Welcome to my studio diary. I'm a 22 year old artist from Cheshire, England and you can call me Vicky. Follow me as I navigate the absurdities of life and the world of art. INSTAGRAM @victoriadalecreative

summary: Just a piece I've been working on for too long( anything that could go wrong, went wrong). I'm happy to finally be done with it...
body:
Just a piece I’ve been working on for too long( anything that could go wrong, went wrong). I’m happy to finally be done with it and on to the next project.

I wanted to focus on more background art and decided to continue on with Beatrice and the library dragon. I wanted to visualize part of the cave the dragon might store her books. Beatrice of course came along for a visit to the dragon’s library.
